                </div>

                <div class="rounded-lg bg-white p-4 text-center shadow-md flex flex-col items-center">
                    <div class="mb-2 text-4xl">🚨</div>
                    <h3 class="mb-2 font-bold">Fake Courier/Delivery</h3>
